<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạảr̊ḍay̱ bimar̊ạảy̱ muḥayãạ
 muf̊tadī ạl̊basẖari
 lil̊qal̊bi fī dẖā ạl̊muḥayãạ
 gẖāyaẗu ạl̊waṭari

[V2]
 2- ại̹nĩy ạủsalĩmuhu naf̊sī
 bijum̊latihā
 fīhi ạlsũrūru wafīhi
 bah̊jaẗu ạlnãẓari

[V3]
 3- ại̹n̊ ḥalã fī muh̊jatī
 ḥubaⁿ̃ạ wabārakanī
 ṣārat̊ ḥayātī ḥayāẗa
 ạl̊kẖiṣ̊bi wāltẖãmari

[V4]
 4- fālsĩj̊nu yum̊sī bihi
 raẘḍaⁿạ, maḥāsinuhu
 tas̊bī wataz̊rī sanaⁿy̱
 biạlsẖãm̊si wāl̊qamari

[V5]
 5- lạa far̊qa fī maẘḍiʿiⁿ
 ʿin̊dī walạ zamani
 mā dāma fīã yaqūdu
 ạlnãf̊sa lilẓãfari</lyrics>
<title>ạ̉rḍy̱ bmrạ̉y̱ mḥyạ mftdy ạlbsẖr</title>
</song>